<% provide(:title, 'Manual Review Notification') %>
<h1>Manual Review Notification</h1>
<p>Dear <%= @user.name %>,</p>
<p>Your KYC documents have been received and are currently under manual review. This process may take some time, we appreciate your patience.</p>
<% if @user.kyc_documents.any? { |doc| doc.status == 'verified' } %>
  <p>We are pleased to inform you that your KYC documents have been manually verified and your KYC status has been updated. You can now proceed with your transactions.</p>
<% else %>
  <p>We will notify you once the review is complete and your KYC status has been updated.</p>
<% end %>
<p>Thank you for your understanding.</p>
<p>Best regards,</p>
<p>Your Team</p>
